href="#_ednref1" name="_edn1" title="" id="_edn1">1</a>] http://jvi.asm.org/content/77/18/9733</p></p></div><div
id="edn2"><p>[<a
href="#_ednref2" name="_edn2" title="" id="_edn2">2</a>] Pathogen Safety Data Sheet of Canada; http://wwCw.phac-aspc.gc.ca/lab-bio/res/psds-ftss/ebola-eng.php</p></p></div><div
